{"tid":380974,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"如果呢個世界真係有外星人地球一早就消滅咗啦，仲有人咩","createTime":"2017-08-30T14:10:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-06T14:28:46.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"53e6899e0213c8191cf7b36b40968026dec0f3ad","tid":380974,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T14:10:08.000Z","msg":"咁咪姐係証明呢個世界無外星人囉，就算有，都會喺另一個次元，神咁辛苦創造我哋出嚟，無理由陷入險境，係咪？"},{"pid":"3b2ce8d92c77a2f67af384195fe0c67b0ec634a5","tid":380974,"uid":57418,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T17:16:08.000Z","msg":"點解有外星人我地就一定死硬？<br />\n如果我地仲存在而又有外星人既話可能係以下幾種情況<br />\n外星生物仲未進化到有文明，所以搵唔到我地<br />\n外星已經發展到文明，科技程度或者比我的高或低，但同我地一樣因為宇宙真係太大被局限左，所以搵唔到我地<br />\n外星文明比我地勁好多，已經發現我地，但覺得我地對佢地完全沒威脅，就好似我地唔會特登搞死d蜜蜂螞蟻一樣<br />\n<br />\nbtw又係你條死耶撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18bdfd58d80c393581051719ea51c5d46022c36b","tid":380974,"uid":125262,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T17:20:03.000Z","msg":"見到最尾個句已經知道唔洗討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0375939f206ed2d1bf7f5d02d7343ffddb39771a","tid":380974,"uid":7948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T17:45:14.000Z","msg":"可唔可外星人對人類好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e274c528f52fdd3de3304f32ceee1f77abea74ae","tid":380974,"uid":113921,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T17:51:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">神</span><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你老味臭閪</span></span>"},{"pid":"009b71fbc5371a1a55267e3fd963d4e5b195b822","tid":380974,"uid":33059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T17:53:23.000Z","msg":"有無睇過阿凡達，<br />\n外星人好廢架"},{"pid":"7e5e0c9fea435b719efae9fc3f4f4f7c4922408c","tid":380974,"uid":118502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T17:56:38.