g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"309ba712eccc23afb2c6f3a9290c1224cd9c319d","tid":380974,"uid":27728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T10:28:11.000Z","msg":"神就或者有既 <br />\n<br />\n但如果你所講既神係天主既話<br />\n<br />\n我就可以肯定係無，加多句屌你老母"},{"pid":"7d82112d4dd8ae174d4d28fea070e3392ac4654e","tid":380974,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T10:29:11.000Z","msg":"世界有三大教<br />\n伊斯蘭(肯定唔會信)<br />\n基督教/天主教(情感上比較信呢個)<br />\n佛教(可信可唔信 當做一門哲學都得 隨你)<br />\n<br />\n無神論(科學理性上推動 覺得一切皆可由科學解釋)<br />\n不可知論(科學始終有限制 例如生命如何誕生根本無從得知 大自然太神奇 所以覺得世界一定有神 但唔係呢個世界人類認為嘅任何一個神)<br />\n<br />\n自己曾經留過嘅9up comment<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90bf7c9b0bec0de61b13c60299fa1e888d074d1a","tid":380974,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T07:57:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d2992855e699098c536fe11a1992dd1719cdcca","tid":380974,"uid":7789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T08:04:42.000Z","msg":"朗拿度係度咁耐都冇咩事，仲比左好多好波我地睇"},{"pid":"38530167f1aac963305c097292b7e751b2f58b5c","tid":380974,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T14:09:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d60aaf61c4e16587d43cb843fda1e120f8ff11b","tid":380974,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T19:09:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06ce1af1f20bf1c5400762b0eb35c928149d9db6","tid":380974,"uid":13281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T19:15:00.000Z","msg":"人類係唔會殺晒d猩猩馬騮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c30906fbea7128f0792ea90d1695d5dfe1646719","tid":380974,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T20:49:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21acbe63776c7d516f7a6c62f624fc9f3c3854b0","tid":380974,"uid":103259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T11:47:11.000Z","msg":"係外星人眼中 地球人其實先係外星人<br />\n咁你有冇聽過地球人殺哂外星人？"},{"pid":"9ade35a88b413dd94abf120d634d6b0ecffa523d","tid":380974,"uid":35317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T14:15:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>世界有三大教<br />\n伊斯蘭(肯定唔會信)<br />\n基督教/天主教(情感上比較信呢個)<br />\n佛教(可信可唔信 當做一門哲學都得 隨你)<br />\n<br />\n無神論(科學理性上推動 覺得一切皆可由科學解釋)<br />\n不可知論(科學始終有限制 例如生命如何誕生根本無從得知 大自然太神奇 所以覺得世界一定有神 但唔係呢個世界人類認為嘅任何一個神)<br />\n<br />\n自己曾經留過嘅9up comment<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n非激進伊斯蘭同基督教有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}